title New Note Sequence

note left of Browser: save button on form is clicked.
Browser->Server: User input sent as an HTTP POST request to /new_note
note right of Server: Data from POST-request body is added to notes array
Server->Browser: Response is HTTP 302 (URL redirect) to reload the notes page

